				<td colspan="2"><span>I got my lvl 61 song and the two +14 Stat augs.  Now I'm stockpiling crystals as I level up to 70.
<br />

<br />
My current weapons are Mace of Memories and Singing Short Sword (see magelo profile)
<br />

<br />
http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1169856
<br />

<br />
I was thinking about bagging both of them in favor of DoN weapons because I'm in a non-raiding guild and primaly do single group stuff and DoN.  Is this a valid assumption, or is there some single group weapons I should consider?
<br />

<br />
Below are some possible choices, and I was wondering what two weapons you would recommend (this assumes I would get worn instrument mods to replace what I'm missing from bagging the epic).  Note: I left off a few that had the big anger procs on them as I didn't think it woudl be a wise choice.
<br />

<br />
Cold Iron Hammer 
<br />
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP
<br />
Slot: PRIMARY SECONDARY
<br />
Skill: 1H Blunt Atk Delay: 20
<br />
