				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: DoN Weapon Choices - 340 crystals<a name="75925"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 28 05 12:28 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Anger procs arent necessarily bad to have.  Bards have a reduced aggro on procs, even with a BoC( i think thats the one that drops from AoW) a bard would have a hard time getting aggro.  Now, i wouldnt use one as a primary weapon in combat, but every once in a while i need to get aggro, and the stun/anger procs are/would be nice to have.  Since most of our damage tends to come from procs( unless you are have really good gear), i would go for those weapons would have the high end procs over the dmg/delay ratio.  The cut Stone shortsword and gold dragon mace would be my choices, This assumes you have instrument mods worn elsewhere of course.</span></td>
