				<td colspan="2"><span>Yes, the Type 9 aug slots were added to all the DoN Armor and Weapons (at least the ones I looked at) in the 5/11/05 patch.
<br />

<br />
This can make for some pretty nice gear for the casual/non-raiding player; however, the type 9 Augs are bit pricey from a crystal standpoint.   Some were in the 450 range and many were in the 680 range.
<br />

<br />
The weapon I described would cost 1,305 crystals.  
<br />

<br />
Cold Iron Hammer - 340 crystals
<br />
Life Sap II (type 4 aug) - 285 crystals
<br />
+1 DMG +1 Magic DMG (type 9 aug) - 680 crystals
<br />

<br />
On Bristlebane server that would be in excess of 300K plat if you were to actually buy the crystals instead of earning them through adventures.  
<br />

<br />
Fortunately, I have a little over 900 crystals saved, now I'm just grinding and saving cyrstals for another 3 yellow so I can actually equip the weapon at lvl 70.</span></td>
